Project	name: Renesas_MCU_uPD70F3376_Switch_Matrix_Controller
Chip        : Renesas V850ES/FG3  uPD70F3376

Development environment : Renesas CubeSuite+ IDE
Programming language    : ANSI C and Renesas assembly programming language
Hareware configurator   : Applilet
Framwork code Auto-generator tool : Applilet

Project description	    : 
    To develop a MCU firmware, to implement these features and functions 
    as below :
    (1).  Control switch-relay-matrix, to switch ON/OFF each channel;
    (2).  Digital OUTPUT, to drive exterior actuator;
    (3).  Digital INPUT, to detect the state of exterior sensor;
    (4).  Communicate with PC host through serial interface, programmable 
          controller;
    (5).  CAN bus transceiver and analyzer, transmitting and receiving CAN 
          telegram, plus telegtam parsing;
    (6).  LIN bus transceiver and analyzer, transmitting, receiving and 
          parsing LIN telegram;
    (7).  ADC acquiring, to measure the analogue voltage and current in the 
          DUT circuit;
    (8).  DAC driving, to output the DC voltage(on demand) to DUT circuit;
    (9).  PWM waveform output,  PWM stimulus output to DUT circuit;

	
Project develop leader  : Henry Xing
Hardware designer       : Henry Xing,   Neil Wu
Software developer      : Xu Zan

